"; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="3" id="3-skip-the-fancy-hotel-3" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">3. Skip the fancy hotel</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image-large on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static2.businessinsider.com/image/590b5e4cfcd8eb4c018b50f6-1200/3-skip-the-fancy-hotel.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="3. Skip the fancy hotel" border="0" class="slide-image-large on-image" /></div><span class="caption-source"><span class="caption">You won't spend all your time at the hotel so it doesn't need to be over-the-top.</span><span><span class="source"><span><a href="http://www.hotels.com/ho543033/the-m-resort-spa-casino-henderson-united-states-of-america/">Hotels.com</a></span></span></span></span></div> <p>Unless you're going on a vacation strictly to experience an epic hotel or resort, Sean suggests sticking to value hotels, Airbnbs, hostels, and even places with shared bathrooms.</p> <p>"A hotel is a place to sleep, and your vacation will be similar no matter how fancy the downstairs lobby. I've found the expensive hotels to be overrated, and their price tags can often fund another vacation entirely," he said.</p> <p>That said, if you're someone who enjoys a little more luxury in your accommodations, consider setting up a rewards account with a major hotel chain. If you travel frequently for work or don't mind spending more up front, you could rack up a few free nights a year in a more luxurious hotel, Sean said.</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "3. Skip the fancy hotel"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "A 27-year-old who saves 65% of his income shares his 7 best tips for traveling on a budget"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/millennial-super-saver-shares-7-best-tips-for-traveling-on-a-budget-2017-5/#3-skip-the-fancy-hotel-3"; curSlideObj.anchor = "3-skip-the-fancy-hotel-3"; curSlideObj.index = 2; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#3-skip-the-fancy-hotel-3";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="4" id="4-always-opt-for-the-free-breakfast-4" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">4. Always opt for the free breakfast</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image-large on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static3.businessinsider.com/image/590b5e8afcd8eb1e038b5135-1200/4-always-opt-for-the-free-breakfast.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="4. Always opt for the free breakfast" border="0" class="slide-image-large on-image" /></div><span class="caption-source"><span class="caption">Complimentary breakfast is a great perk.</span><span><span class="source"><span>Unsplash / Helio Ha</span></span></span></span></div><p><span>"All else being equal, I choose the hotel with a free breakfast," says Sean. "Starting the day with a huge breakfast can save lots of money on breakfast </span><em>and</em><span> lunch, which can really add up over a few days."</span></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "4. Always opt for the free breakfast"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "A 27-year-old who saves 65% of his income shares his 7 best tips for traveling on a budget"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/millennial-super-saver-shares-7-best-tips-for-traveling-on-a-budget-2017-5/#4-always-opt-for-the-free-breakfast-4"; curSlideObj.anchor = "4-always-opt-for-the-free-breakfast-4"; curSlideObj.index = 3; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#4-always-opt-for-the-free-breakfast-4";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
