"; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="5" id="5-take-advantage-of-credit-card-perks-5" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">5. Take advantage of credit card perks</h3> <p>The <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/most-powerful-travel-rewards-credit-cards-2017-3">travel credit card space is becoming increasingly competitive</a> and major banks are releasing new perks and benefits regularly to capture loyal customers — and that's good news for travelers.</p> <p>"Periodically signing up for credit card bonus offers and responsibly using the card is a great way to rack up free flights and hotels," Sean said. "I <a href="http://mymoneywizard.com/chase-sapphire-reserve-review/">wrote about the now expired </a><span><a href="http://mymoneywizard.com/chase-sapphire-reserve-review/">100,000 point offer</a> for the Chase Sapphire Reserve, which was enough to fund a few reasonable vacations outright."</span></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "5. Take advantage of credit card perks"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "A 27-year-old who saves 65% of his income shares his 7 best tips for traveling on a budget"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/millennial-super-saver-shares-7-best-tips-for-traveling-on-a-budget-2017-5/#5-take-advantage-of-credit-card-perks-5"; curSlideObj.anchor = "5-take-advantage-of-credit-card-perks-5"; curSlideObj.index = 4; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#5-take-advantage-of-credit-card-perks-5";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="6" id="6-look-for-dining-deals-6" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">6. Look for dining deals</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image-large on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static4.businessinsider.com/image/590b61f62ceae91d008b514a-1200/6-look-for-dining-deals.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="6. Look for dining deals" border="0" class="slide-image-large on-image" /></div><span class="caption-source"><span class="caption">Not every meal has to break the bank.</span><span><span class="source"><span><a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/dominicspics/1135876473/">Flickr/Dominic Alves</a></span></span></span></span></div> <p>It's no secret that dining out for every meal <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/how-americans-spend-most-of-their-money-2017-1">can add up</a>.</p> <p>"I check <a href="http://groupon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://Groupon.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1493923331821000&amp;usg=AFQjCNEYNm-Qi36ikJn_Y2JeF8W9XWQDMw">Groupon.com</a> for deals wherever I'm traveling to, which can save big while still providing the dinning out experience," Sean said. "Many cities also have local coupon books, which can be a good source for cheap dinners and activities."</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "6. Look for dining deals"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "A 27-year-old who saves 65% of his income shares his 7 best tips for traveling on a budget"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/millennial-super-saver-shares-7-best-tips-for-traveling-on-a-budget-2017-5/#6-look-for-dining-deals-6"; curSlideObj.anchor = "6-look-for-dining-deals-6"; curSlideObj.index = 5; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#6-look-for-dining-deals-6";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="7" id="7-pass-on-the-tourist-traps-7" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">7. Pass on the tourist traps</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image-large on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/590b5eeffcd8eb0c4a8b4b48-1200/7-pass-on-the-tourist-traps.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="7. Pass on the tourist traps" border="0" class="slide-image-large on-image" /></div><span class="caption-source"><span class="caption">Tourist traps like Times Square tend to be both overcrowded and overpriced. A little research will unearth a more authentic and cost friendly alternative.</span><span><span class="source"><span>Getty Images</span></span></span></span></div> <p>A free hike, museum, or public landmark is almost always a better experience than the high-priced tourist trap, Sean said.</p> <p>"I always check <a href="http://tripadvisor.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-saferedirecturl="https://www.google.com/url?hl=en&amp;q=http://Tripadvisor.com&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1493923331821000&amp;usg=AFQjCNHcT_9o0PMEEKMoneQ0Bv9FTjmI3g">Tripadvisor.com</a>'s 'Things to do' or talk to locals once I arrive, in order to brainstorm ideas of fun, cheap activities. Beware of guided tours. They're usually a way to charge lots of money for something that is otherwise free," he said.</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "7. Pass on the tourist traps"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "A 27-year-old who saves 65% of his income shares his 7 best tips for traveling on a budget"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/millennial-super-saver-shares-7-best-tips-for-traveling-on-a-budget-2017-5/#7-pass-on-the-tourist-traps-7"; curSlideObj.anchor = "7-pass-on-the-tourist-traps-7"; curSlideObj.index = 6; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#7-pass-on-the-tourist-traps-7";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> </div> </div> </div> <!-- See Also Text Links --> <div id="see-also-links" class="see-also"> <h3><span class="all-caps">SEE ALSO:</span> <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/what-is-round-the-world-airline-ticket-2017-4" >Thanks to a little-known airline hack, traveling around the world could be cheaper than you realize</a> </h3> <h3><span class="all-caps">SEE ALSO:</span> <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/best-pieces-of-saving-advice-from-real-people-who-banked-a-fortune-2017-4" >The 8 best pieces of saving advice from real people who banked a fortune</a> </h3> </div> <!-- / See Also Text Links --

static1.businessinsider.com/image/55e5d0099dd7cc16008b7487-913-685/new%20york%20city-2.jpg" alt="New York City" data-mce-source="Flickr / kiki99"><span class="source-only"><span class="source"><span>Flickr / kiki99</span></span></span></span><p></span></span>If you're new to New York City, you can be sure you're not alone. With more than 8.5 million residents, NYC is filled with natives and newbies alike. </p> <p>As a NYC transplant myself, I've recently decided to ditch the travel guides for books that give a little more life to the concrete jungle. </p> <p>Here are a few of my favorites.  </p> <div class="slideshow-content slide-intro-bottom"> <h4> View As: <a href="#" onclick="return false;" class="sl-start border-right disabled">One Page</a> <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9?op=0#/#my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city-1" class="sl-start href-swap">Slides</a> </h4> </div> <div class="clearfix"></div> </div> <br class="clear-both" /> <script type="text/javascript"> BI.vaop = []; </script> <!-- Slides --> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="1" id="my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city-1" class="slide-module first-slide clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">My First New York: Early Adventures in the Big City</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image"><div><img data-src="http://static1.businessinsider.com/image/55e5a9cc9dd7cc16008b7345-1200/my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="My First New York: Early Adventures in the Big City" border="0" class="slide-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Amazon.com</span></span></span></span></div> <p>The editors of New York Magazine compiled this poignant pocket book of first experiences in the city as told by a host of its most iconic residents — from Liza Minnelli to Andy Samberg. The 56 stories that make up "My First New York" are a testament to time and a reminder that even the most successful New Yorkers were once outsiders.</p> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/My-First-New-York-Adventures/dp/0061963941">Buy it on Amazon »</a> </p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "My First New York: Early Adventures in the Big City"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "The 6 best books to pick up if you just moved to New York City"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9/#my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city-1"; curSlideObj.anchor = "my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city-1"; curSlideObj.index = 0; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#my-first-new-york-early-adventures-in-the-big-city-1";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="2" id="every-person-in-new-york-2" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">Every Person in New York</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image"><div><img data-src="http://static2.businessinsider.com/image/55e5aa41bd86ef10008b738c-1200/every-person-in-new-york.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="Every Person in New York" border="0" class="slide-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Amazon</span></span></span></span></div> <p>Jason Polan is an artist on a mission to sketch every single person in New York City. This recently released collection is the first what is expected to be a never-ending series.</p> <p>Much like the portraitist behind <a href="http://www.humansofnewyork.com/">Humans of New York</a>, Polan's accounts of the folks he sees on subways, street corners, and in museums are both endearing and honest. "Every Person in New York" is a reminder that part of the charm of New York City is its inhabitants. </p> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Every-Person-York-Jason-Polan/dp/1452128235">Buy it on Amazon »</a></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "Every Person in New York"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "The 6 best books to pick up if you just moved to New York City"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9/#every-person-in-new-york-2"; curSlideObj.anchor = "every-person-in-new-york-2"; curSlideObj.index = 1; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#every-person-in-new-york-2";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
