tainer slide-image"><div><img data-src="http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/55e5bc45bd86ef17008b73f9-1200/the-catcher-in-the-rye.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="The Catcher in the Rye" border="0" class="slide-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Amazon</span></span></span></span></div> <p>I'm adding a novel into the mix because what's more New York than J.D. Salinger's "Catcher in the Rye"? It's the kind of New York coming-of-age tale that roars to life when you're actually sitting in Central Park reading about the city surrounding you. Holden Caulfield's troubles have a whole new impact when you re-read the book as a newly minted New Yorker. </p> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Catcher-Rye-J-D-Salinger/dp/0316769487">Buy it on Amazon »</a></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "The Catcher in the Rye"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "The 6 best books to pick up if you just moved to New York City"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9/#the-catcher-in-the-rye-4"; curSlideObj.anchor = "the-catcher-in-the-rye-4"; curSlideObj.index = 3; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#the-catcher-in-the-rye-4";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
