"; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="5" id="nyc-basic-tips-and-etiquette-5" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">NYC Basic Tips and Etiquette</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static3.businessinsider.com/image/55e5c6bd9dd7cc21008b74c5-1200/nyc-basic-tips-and-etiquette.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="NYC Basic Tips and Etiquette" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Amazon</span></span></span></span></div> <p>Nathan Pyle, a New York City transplant, was so fascinated by the city's culture that he decided to draw up a visual rule book that covers everything from how to ride a subway to where to find the West Village.</p> <p>The book brims with 136 tips and witty illustrations that entertain and inform even the most clueless of New Yorkers. Even better still, "NYC Basic Tips and Etiquette" is available as an animated e-book — including GIFs, naturally. </p> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Basic-Tips-Etiquette-Nathan-Pyle/dp/0062303112/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1397755955&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=nyc+basic+tips+and+etiquette&amp;tag=bisafetynet-20">Buy it on Amazon »</a></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "NYC Basic Tips and Etiquette"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "The 6 best books to pick up if you just moved to New York City"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9/#nyc-basic-tips-and-etiquette-5"; curSlideObj.anchor = "nyc-basic-tips-and-etiquette-5"; curSlideObj.index = 4; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#nyc-basic-tips-and-etiquette-5";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="6" id="the-film-lovers-new-york-6" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">The Film Lover's New York</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image"><div><img data-src="http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/55e5c6d59dd7cc0f008b7502-1200/the-film-lovers-new-york.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="The Film Lover's New York" border="0" class="slide-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Amazon</span></span></span></span></div> <p>One of the coolest experiences of living in New York City is spotting a setting you've seen in a film, whether it be a bench in Central Park or a storefront on Fifth Avenue.</p> <p>"The Film Lover's New York" is a comprehensive guide to the most famous movies and television shows filmed in NYC, from "The Great Gatsby" to "Sex and the City." It's a wonderfully inventive way to explore the city on a Saturday afternoon.</p> <p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/The-Film-Lovers-New-York/dp/2812309865">Buy it on Amazon »</a></p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "The Film Lover's New York"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "The 6 best books to pick up if you just moved to New York City"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/6-books-every-new-new-yorker-should-read-2015-9/#the-film-lovers-new-york-6"; curSlideObj.anchor = "the-film-lovers-new-york-6"; curSlideObj.index = 5; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#the-film-lovers-new-york-6";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> </div> </div> </div> <!-- See Also Text Links --> <div id="see-also-links" class="see-also"> <h3><span class="all-caps">SEE ALSO:</span> <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/photos-of-old-new-york-2015-8" >Stunning photos of one of the last vestiges of old New York</a> </h3> <h3><span class="all-caps">FOLLOW:</span> <a href="https://twitter.com/BI_TheLife" >Business Insider Lifestyle is on Twitter!</a> </h3> </div> <!-- / See Also Text Links --

static3.businessinsider.com/image/56846caae6183e591e8b5dc3-2048-1536/world%20changing%20man%20globe.jpg" alt="world changing man globe" data-mce-source="Flickr/https://www.flickr.com/photos/foxspain/3219577797/"><span class="source-only"><span class="source"><span>Flickr/<a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/foxspain/3219577797/">www.flickr.com</a></span></span></span></span><p></span></span>It's become a Silicon Valley cliche to talk changing the world by launching a startup. Most startups don't do anything quite that dramatic.</p> <p>But some of them do.</p> <p>As we march into 2016, it's a good time to look over the tech landscape to pinpoint the ones on track to change the business world, particularly the area of enterprise computing, the tech that runs our companies.</p> <p>That's exactly what Dell has done with its <a href="http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20151217005096/en/Dell-Founders-50-Spotlights-Startups-Innovative-Solutions">third-annual Founders 50 list.</a> This is a list of global startups that are "disrupting their respective industries and poised to be household names in the coming years," as Dell describes them.</p> <p>We're not sure they're going to become household names like Google or Microsoft. But they sure are developing some interesting and game-changing technologies worth watching this year and beyond. </p> <div class="slideshow-content slide-intro-bottom"> <h4> View As: <a href="#" onclick="return false;" class="sl-start border-right disabled">One Page</a> <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12?op=0#/#a3cube-super-fast-networks-1" class="sl-start href-swap">Slides</a> </h4> </div> <div class="clearfix"></div> </div> <br class="clear-both" /> <script type="text/javascript"> BI.vaop = []; </script> <!-- Slides --> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="1" id="a3cube-super-fast-networks-1" class="slide-module first-slide clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">A3Cube: super fast networks</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static1.businessinsider.com/image/56846f62c08a80872f8b5294-1200/a3cube-super-fast-networks.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="A3Cube: super fast networks" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span><a href="http://a3cube-inc.com/">A3CUBE</a></span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://a3cube-inc.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">A3Cube</a></p> <p>A3Cube has created a very fast type of combined computer/storage device.</p> <p>It is designed for demanding "high-performance computing" for big data, analytics and virtualization, while reducing power consumption.</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "A3Cube: super fast networks"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#a3cube-super-fast-networks-1"; curSlideObj.anchor = "a3cube-super-fast-networks-1"; curSlideObj.index = 0; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#a3cube-super-fast-networks-1";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="2" id="alienvault-making-sense-of-security-data-2" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">AlienVault: making sense of security data</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static6.businessinsider.com/image/56980561e6183ebe4a8b936c-1200/alienvault-making-sense-of-security-data.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="AlienVault: making sense of security data" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>AlienVault</span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://www.alienvault.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">AlienVault</a></p> <p>AlienVault is the creator of a popular security tool known as the Open Source Security Information Management (OSSIM). It helps companies make sense of the huge amounts of data generated by their many security products.</p> <p>It also mans a forum called the "<span>Open Threat Exchange" where security pros can share information on hacks and threats as they find them.</span></p> <p>As an open source tool, OSSIM can be downloaded and used for free, and has been by over 195,000 security pros, <a href="https://www.alienvault.com/products/ossim">the company says</a>. <span>AlienVault provides commercial support for it, adding features and making it easier for enterprise IT teams to use it.</span></p> <p> </p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "AlienVault: making sense of security data"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#alienvault-making-sense-of-security-data-2"; curSlideObj.anchor = "alienvault-making-sense-of-security-data-2"; curSlideObj.index = 1; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#alienvault-making-sense-of-security-data-2";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
