"; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="35" id="nexenta-ushering-in-open-source-storage-35" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">Nexenta: ushering in open-source storage</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static3.businessinsider.com/image/569437d4c08a809e2f8b61d7-1200/nexenta-ushering-in-open-source-storage.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="Nexenta: ushering in open-source storage" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Nexenta</span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://www.nexenta.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Nexenta Systems</a> </p> <p>Nexenta is proving that storage doesn't have to be locked away in the expensive proprietary technologies owned by storage vendors.</p> <p>It focuses on what's known as "software-defined storage" using open source technologies. (Open source allows anyone to see and modify the code and share changes with others.)</p> <p>It's come up with its own name for this "Open Software-Defined Storage or OpenSDS" but the name is less important than this: its storage works with just about every other major vendors data center tech including <a href="http://finapps.forbes.com/finapps/jsp/finance/compinfo/CIAtAGlance.jsp?tkr=vmw&amp;tab=searchtabquotesdark">VMware</a>, Citrix, Cloudstack, <a href="http://finapps.forbes.com/finapps/jsp/finance/compinfo/CIAtAGlance.jsp?tkr=msft&amp;tab=searchtabquotesdark">Microsoft</a>, Openstack and <a href="http://finapps.forbes.com/finapps/jsp/finance/compinfo/CIAtAGlance.jsp?tkr=amzn&amp;tab=searchtabquotesdark">Amazon Web Services</a>.</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "Nexenta: ushering in open-source storage"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#nexenta-ushering-in-open-source-storage-35"; curSlideObj.anchor = "nexenta-ushering-in-open-source-storage-35"; curSlideObj.index = 34; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#nexenta-ushering-in-open-source-storage-35";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads =""; BI.vaop.push(curSlideObj); </script> <!-- add the slide content to the slide html object --> <div data-slide="36" id="nutanix-king-of-the-hyperconverged-data-center-36" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">Nutanix: king of the 'hyperconverged' data center</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static2.businessinsider.com/image/569439b1c08a8036008b8b6b-1200/nutanix-king-of-the-hyperconverged-data-center.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="Nutanix: king of the 'hyperconverged' data center" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Nutanix</span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://www.nutanix.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Nutanix</a></p> <p>Nutanix is one of the companies that has changed how enterprises build their data centers. It helped create, and leads, a young market called "hyperconverged."</p> <p>It's a way to provide enterprise storage that gloms together a computer, the storage and the software that makes computers more efficient known as "virtualization." </p> <p>A company stacks its "hyperconverged" units together  to grow their data centers, which reduces power, space and makes storage easier to manage.</p> <p>Nutanix is one of the much-awaited IPOs of <a href="http://www.businessinsider.com/nutanix-files-s1-2015-12">2016 that recently filed its IPO paperwork</a>.</p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "Nutanix: king of the 'hyperconverged' data center"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#nutanix-king-of-the-hyperconverged-data-center-36"; curSlideObj.anchor = "nutanix-king-of-the-hyperconverged-data-center-36"; curSlideObj.index = 35; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#nutanix-king-of-the-hyperconverged-data-center-36";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
