orks-38" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">Plexxi: application-aware software-defined networks</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static5.businessinsider.com/image/5696e15fc08a80ae2f8b86f9-1200/plexxi-application-aware-software-defined-networks.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="Plexxi: application-aware software-defined networks" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>Plexxi</span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://www.plexxi.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Plexxi</a></p> <p>Plexxi is one of the startups working in a hot area called "software-defined networking." That's when a corporate network can be controlled and changed via software automating many tasks. This is instead of the old-fashoned way, physically moving devices that are attached to physical wires.</p> <p>There's a ton of networking companies all doing SDN in some shape or form. Plexxi is unique because its technology works with a super fast type of network, optical networking, and it takes into account the application that is being accessed over the network.</p> <p> </p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "Plexxi: application-aware software-defined networks"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#plexxi-application-aware-software-defined-networks-38"; curSlideObj.anchor = "plexxi-application-aware-software-defined-networks-38"; curSlideObj.index = 37; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#plexxi-application-aware-software-defined-networks-38";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
