st-robotic-interior-designer-44" class="slide-module clearfix vaop-breakpoint"> <!-- add title if exists --> <h3 class="slide-title">SNapKin: the first robotic interior designer</h3> <div class="KonaFilter image-container slide-image on-image"><div><img data-src="http://static4.businessinsider.com/image/569852dfc08a80d7118b9b58-1200/snapkin-the-first-robotic-interior-designer.jpg" src="/assets/images/logos/BI-placeholder.svg" alt="SNapKin: the first robotic interior designer" border="0" class="slide-image on-image" /></div><span class="source-only"><span><span class="source"><span>SnapKin</span></span></span></span></div> <p><a href="http://www.snapkin.fr/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">SNapKin</a></p> <p>SNapKin calls itself the first robotic interior designer. It’s a tool that you place in the middle of the room. It swivels around and takes a 3D measurement of the space.</p> <p>From that measurement, a basic floor plan can be compiled, quotes can be collected, and so on. </p> </div> <script type="text/javascript"> var curSlideObj = {}; curSlideObj.title = "SNapKin: the first robotic interior designer"; curSlideObj.postTitle = "50 enterprise startups you've probably never heard of who really are changing the world"; curSlideObj.url = "http://www.businessinsider.com/50-game-changing-enterprise-startups-2015-12/#snapkin-the-first-robotic-interior-designer-44"; curSlideObj.anchor = "snapkin-the-first-robotic-interior-designer-44"; curSlideObj.index = 43; curSlideObj.embeds = {}; curSlideObj.slideShareButtonsEnabled = true; curSlideObj.name ="/#snapkin-the-first-robotic-interior-designer-44";curSlideObj.embeds =[];curSlideObj.html ="";curSlideObj.ads ="
